# SouthernReport Help Center

Welcome to the SouthernReport Help Center. Find quick answers below, or reach us via [Support](SUPPORT.md).

---

## 👤 Getting Started

**How do I create an account?**
Sign up from the homepage, then open your profile menu to access My Profile, Create Post, Signature Card, and your Earnings Dashboard.

**Is SouthernReport free to use?**
Yes — reading news, publishing posts, browsing jobs, and applying for jobs are all free.

---

## ✍️ Publishing

**How do I publish a post?**
1. Tap **+ Create** in the navigation bar.
2. Choose **Article** or **Video**.
3. Add a compelling headline, select a category, upload a featured image (or paste an image URL), and write a short excerpt.
4. Publish — your post goes live and starts counting views immediately.

**What is a Signature Card?**
A Signature Card is your branded publisher identity on SouthernReport. It builds trust with readers and makes your posts recognizable.

**What is the Video Analyser?**
An AI tool that transcribes any video to text. Connect your YouTube channel to auto-upload videos directly from the platform.

---

## 💰 Earnings

**How much do I earn?**
The current rate is **₦200 per 1,000 views** on your published content.

**When can I cash out?**
Once your balance crosses the minimum payout threshold of **1,000 views**.

**Where do I track my earnings?**
Open your profile menu → **Earnings Dashboard** to see total views, total earnings, amount paid out, and current balance — all in real time.

---

## 💼 Jobs

**How do I post a job?**
Go to the **Jobs** section and create a listing — it takes only a few minutes.

**How do I apply for a job?**
Browse open positions in the **Jobs** section and apply directly on the platform.

---

## 📱 App & Notifications

**Can I install SouthernReport on my phone?**
Yes. SouthernReport is an installable PWA — tap **Install App** when the banner appears to get breaking news alerts on your home screen.

---

Still stuck? Head to [Support](SUPPORT.md) — we're happy to help.
